{"surah":{"number":69,"name":"الحاقة","englishName":"Al-Haqqah","englishTranslation":"The Reality","ayahCount":52},"sources":["Quran.com API v4 (word-by-word Uthmani + English glosses + word audio)","AlQuran.cloud / Tanzil quran-uthmani (independent text verification)","AlQuran.cloud / Saheeh International (flowing English translation)","Quranic Arabic Corpus morphology (word roots)"],"generatedAt":"2026-07-03T04:01:30.348Z","ayahs":[{"number":1,"translation":"The Inevitable Reality -","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"ٱلْحَآقَّةُ","english":"The Inevitable Reality","translit":"al-ḥāqatu","root":"حقق"}]},{"number":2,"translation":"What is the Inevitable Reality?","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"مَا","english":"What","translit":"mā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلْحَآقَّةُ","english":"(is) the Inevitable Reality","translit":"l-ḥāqatu","root":"حقق"}]},{"number":3,"translation":"And what can make you know what is the Inevitable Reality?","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَمَآ","english":"And what","translit":"wamā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"أَدْرَىٰكَ","english":"will make you know","translit":"adrāka","root":"دري"},{"position":3,"arabic":"مَا","english":"what","translit":"mā","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"ٱلْحَآقَّةُ","english":"(is) the Inevitable Reality","translit":"l-ḥāqatu","root":"حقق"}]},{"number":4,"translation":"Thamud and 'Aad denied the Striking Calamity.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"كَذَّبَتْ","english":"Denied","translit":"kadhabat","root":"كذب"},{"position":2,"arabic":"ثَمُودُ","english":"Thamud","translit":"thamūdu","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"وَعَادٌۢ","english":"and Aad","translit":"waʿādun","root":"عود"},{"position":4,"arabic":"بِٱلْقَارِعَةِ","english":"the Striking Calamity","translit":"bil-qāriʿati","root":"قرع"}]},{"number":5,"translation":"So as for Thamud, they were destroyed by the overpowering [blast].","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَأَمَّا","english":"So as for","translit":"fa-ammā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"ثَمُودُ","english":"Thamud","translit":"thamūdu","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"فَأُهْلِكُوا۟","english":"they were destroyed","translit":"fa-uh'likū","root":"هلك"},{"position":4,"arabic":"بِٱلطَّاغِيَةِ","english":"by the overpowering (blast)","translit":"bil-ṭāghiyati","root":"طغي"}]},{"number":6,"translation":"And as for 'Aad, they were destroyed by a screaming, violent wind","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَأَمَّا","english":"And as for","translit":"wa-ammā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"عَادٌۭ","english":"Aad","translit":"ʿādun","root":"عود"},{"position":3,"arabic":"فَأُهْلِكُوا۟","english":"they were destroyed","translit":"fa-uh'likū","root":"هلك"},{"position":4,"arabic":"بِرِيحٍۢ","english":"by a wind","translit":"birīḥin","root":"روح"},{"position":5,"arabic":"صَرْصَرٍ","english":"screaming","translit":"ṣarṣarin","root":"صرصر"},{"position":6,"arabic":"عَاتِيَةٍۢ","english":"violent","translit":"ʿātiyatin","root":"عتو"}]},{"number":7,"translation":"Which Allah imposed upon them for seven nights and eight days in succession, so you would see the people therein fallen as if they were hollow trunks of palm trees.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"سَخَّرَهَا","english":"Which He imposed","translit":"sakharahā","root":"سخر"},{"position":2,"arabic":"عَلَيْهِمْ","english":"upon them","translit":"ʿalayhim","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"سَبْعَ","english":"(for) seven","translit":"sabʿa","root":"سبع"},{"position":4,"arabic":"لَيَالٍۢ","english":"nights","translit":"layālin","root":"ليل"},{"position":5,"arabic":"وَثَمَـٰنِيَةَ","english":"and eight","translit":"wathamāniyata","root":"ثمن"},{"position":6,"arabic":"أَيَّامٍ","english":"days","translit":"ayyāmin","root":"يوم"},{"position":7,"arabic":"حُسُومًۭا","english":"(in) succession","translit":"ḥusūman","root":"حسم"},{"position":8,"arabic":"فَتَرَى","english":"so you would see","translit":"fatarā","root":"رأي"},{"position":9,"arabic":"ٱلْقَوْمَ","english":"the people","translit":"l-qawma","root":"قوم"},{"position":10,"arabic":"فِيهَا","english":"therein","translit":"fīhā","root":""},{"position":11,"arabic":"صَرْعَىٰ","english":"fallen","translit":"ṣarʿā","root":"صرع"},{"position":12,"arabic":"كَأَنَّهُمْ","english":"as if they were","translit":"ka-annahum","root":""},{"position":13,"arabic":"أَعْجَازُ","english":"trunks","translit":"aʿjāzu","root":"عجز"},{"position":14,"arabic":"نَخْلٍ","english":"(of) date-palms","translit":"nakhlin","root":"نخل"},{"position":15,"arabic":"خَاوِيَةٍۢ","english":"hollow","translit":"khāwiyatin","root":"خوي"}]},{"number":8,"translation":"Then do you see of them any remains?","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَهَلْ","english":"Then do","translit":"fahal","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"تَرَىٰ","english":"you see","translit":"tarā","root":"رأي"},{"position":3,"arabic":"لَهُم","english":"of them","translit":"lahum","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"مِّنۢ","english":"any","translit":"min","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"بَاقِيَةٍۢ","english":"remains","translit":"bāqiyatin","root":"بقي"}]},{"number":9,"translation":"And there came Pharaoh and those before him and the overturned cities with sin.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَجَآءَ","english":"And came","translit":"wajāa","root":"جيأ"},{"position":2,"arabic":"فِرْعَوْنُ","english":"Firaun","translit":"fir'ʿawnu","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"وَمَن","english":"and (those)","translit":"waman","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"قَبْلَهُۥ","english":"before him","translit":"qablahu","root":"قبل"},{"position":5,"arabic":"وَٱلْمُؤْتَفِكَـٰتُ","english":"and the overturned cities","translit":"wal-mu'tafikātu","root":"أفك"},{"position":6,"arabic":"بِٱلْخَاطِئَةِ","english":"with sin","translit":"bil-khāṭi-ati","root":"خطأ"}]},{"number":10,"translation":"And they disobeyed the messenger of their Lord, so He seized them with a seizure exceeding [in severity].","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَعَصَوْا۟","english":"And they disobeyed","translit":"faʿaṣaw","root":"عصي"},{"position":2,"arabic":"رَسُولَ","english":"(the) Messenger","translit":"rasūla","root":"رسل"},{"position":3,"arabic":"رَبِّهِمْ","english":"(of) their Lord","translit":"rabbihim","root":"ربب"},{"position":4,"arabic":"فَأَخَذَهُمْ","english":"so He seized them","translit":"fa-akhadhahum","root":"أخذ"},{"position":5,"arabic":"أَخْذَةًۭ","english":"(with) a seizure","translit":"akhdhatan","root":"أخذ"},{"position":6,"arabic":"رَّابِيَةً","english":"exceeding","translit":"rābiyatan","root":"ربو"}]},{"number":11,"translation":"Indeed, when the water overflowed, We carried your ancestors in the sailing ship","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"إِنَّا","english":"Indeed, We","translit":"innā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"لَمَّا","english":"when","translit":"lammā","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"طَغَا","english":"overflowed","translit":"ṭaghā","root":"طغي"},{"position":4,"arabic":"ٱلْمَآءُ","english":"the water","translit":"l-māu","root":"موه"},{"position":5,"arabic":"حَمَلْنَـٰكُمْ","english":"We carried you","translit":"ḥamalnākum","root":"حمل"},{"position":6,"arabic":"فِى","english":"in","translit":"fī","root":""},{"position":7,"arabic":"ٱلْجَارِيَةِ","english":"the sailing (ship)","translit":"l-jāriyati","root":"جري"}]},{"number":12,"translation":"That We might make it for you a reminder and [that] a conscious ear would be conscious of it.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"لِنَجْعَلَهَا","english":"That We might make it","translit":"linajʿalahā","root":"جعل"},{"position":2,"arabic":"لَكُمْ","english":"for you","translit":"lakum","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"تَذْكِرَةًۭ","english":"a reminder","translit":"tadhkiratan","root":"ذكر"},{"position":4,"arabic":"وَتَعِيَهَآ","english":"and would be conscious of it","translit":"wataʿiyahā","root":"وعي"},{"position":5,"arabic":"أُذُنٌۭ","english":"an ear","translit":"udhunun","root":"أذن"},{"position":6,"arabic":"وَٰعِيَةٌۭ","english":"conscious","translit":"wāʿiyatun","root":"وعي"}]},{"number":13,"translation":"Then when the Horn is blown with one blast","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَإِذَا","english":"Then when","translit":"fa-idhā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"نُفِخَ","english":"is blown","translit":"nufikha","root":"نفخ"},{"position":3,"arabic":"فِى","english":"in","translit":"fī","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"ٱلصُّورِ","english":"the trumpet","translit":"l-ṣūri","root":"صور"},{"position":5,"arabic":"نَفْخَةٌۭ","english":"a blast","translit":"nafkhatun","root":"نفخ"},{"position":6,"arabic":"وَٰحِدَةٌۭ","english":"single","translit":"wāḥidatun","root":"وحد"}]},{"number":14,"translation":"And the earth and the mountains are lifted and leveled with one blow -","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَحُمِلَتِ","english":"And are lifted","translit":"waḥumilati","root":"حمل"},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلْأَرْضُ","english":"the earth","translit":"l-arḍu","root":"أرض"},{"position":3,"arabic":"وَٱلْجِبَالُ","english":"and the mountains","translit":"wal-jibālu","root":"جبل"},{"position":4,"arabic":"فَدُكَّتَا","english":"and crushed","translit":"fadukkatā","root":"دكك"},{"position":5,"arabic":"دَكَّةًۭ","english":"(with) a crushing","translit":"dakkatan","root":"دكك"},{"position":6,"arabic":"وَٰحِدَةًۭ","english":"single","translit":"wāḥidatan","root":"وحد"}]},{"number":15,"translation":"Then on that Day, the Resurrection will occur,","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَيَوْمَئِذٍۢ","english":"Then (on) that Day","translit":"fayawma-idhin","root":"يوم"},{"position":2,"arabic":"وَقَعَتِ","english":"will occur","translit":"waqaʿati","root":"وقع"},{"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلْوَاقِعَةُ","english":"the Occurrence","translit":"l-wāqiʿatu","root":"وقع"}]},{"number":16,"translation":"And the heaven will split [open], for that Day it is infirm.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَٱنشَقَّتِ","english":"And will split","translit":"wa-inshaqqati","root":"شقق"},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلسَّمَآءُ","english":"the heaven","translit":"l-samāu","root":"سمو"},{"position":3,"arabic":"فَهِىَ","english":"so it","translit":"fahiya","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"يَوْمَئِذٍۢ","english":"(is on) that Day","translit":"yawma-idhin","root":"يوم"},{"position":5,"arabic":"وَاهِيَةٌۭ","english":"frail","translit":"wāhiyatun","root":"وهي"}]},{"number":17,"translation":"And the angels are at its edges. And there will bear the Throne of your Lord above them, that Day, eight [of them].","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَٱلْمَلَكُ","english":"And the Angels","translit":"wal-malaku","root":"ملك"},{"position":2,"arabic":"عَلَىٰٓ","english":"(will be) on","translit":"ʿalā","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"أَرْجَآئِهَا ۚ","english":"its edges","translit":"arjāihā","root":"رجو"},{"position":4,"arabic":"وَيَحْمِلُ","english":"and will bear","translit":"wayaḥmilu","root":"حمل","audio":"wbw/069_017_005.mp3"},{"position":5,"arabic":"عَرْشَ","english":"(the) Throne","translit":"ʿarsha","root":"عرش","audio":"wbw/069_017_006.mp3"},{"position":6,"arabic":"رَبِّكَ","english":"(of) your Lord","translit":"rabbika","root":"ربب","audio":"wbw/069_017_007.mp3"},{"position":7,"arabic":"فَوْقَهُمْ","english":"above them","translit":"fawqahum","root":"فوق","audio":"wbw/069_017_008.mp3"},{"position":8,"arabic":"يَوْمَئِذٍۢ","english":"that Day","translit":"yawma-idhin","root":"يوم","audio":"wbw/069_017_009.mp3"},{"position":9,"arabic":"ثَمَـٰنِيَةٌۭ","english":"eight","translit":"thamāniyatun","root":"ثمن","audio":"wbw/069_017_010.mp3"}]},{"number":18,"translation":"That Day, you will be exhibited [for judgement]; not hidden among you is anything concealed.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"يَوْمَئِذٍۢ","english":"That Day","translit":"yawma-idhin","root":"يوم"},{"position":2,"arabic":"تُعْرَضُونَ","english":"you will be exhibited","translit":"tuʿ'raḍūna","root":"عرض"},{"position":3,"arabic":"لَا","english":"not","translit":"lā","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"تَخْفَىٰ","english":"will be hidden","translit":"takhfā","root":"خفي"},{"position":5,"arabic":"مِنكُمْ","english":"among you","translit":"minkum","root":""},{"position":6,"arabic":"خَافِيَةٌۭ","english":"any secret","translit":"khāfiyatun","root":"خفي"}]},{"number":19,"translation":"So as for he who is given his record in his right hand, he will say, \"Here, read my record!","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَأَمَّا","english":"Then as for","translit":"fa-ammā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"مَنْ","english":"(him) who","translit":"man","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"أُوتِىَ","english":"is given","translit":"ūtiya","root":"أتي"},{"position":4,"arabic":"كِتَـٰبَهُۥ","english":"his record","translit":"kitābahu","root":"كتب"},{"position":5,"arabic":"بِيَمِينِهِۦ","english":"in his right hand","translit":"biyamīnihi","root":"يمن"},{"position":6,"arabic":"فَيَقُولُ","english":"will say","translit":"fayaqūlu","root":"قول"},{"position":7,"arabic":"هَآؤُمُ","english":"Here","translit":"hāumu","root":"هاء"},{"position":8,"arabic":"ٱقْرَءُوا۟","english":"read","translit":"iq'raū","root":"قرأ"},{"position":9,"arabic":"كِتَـٰبِيَهْ","english":"my record","translit":"kitābiyah","root":"كتب"}]},{"number":20,"translation":"Indeed, I was certain that I would be meeting my account.\"","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"إِنِّى","english":"Indeed, I","translit":"innī","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"ظَنَنتُ","english":"was certain","translit":"ẓanantu","root":"ظنن"},{"position":3,"arabic":"أَنِّى","english":"that I","translit":"annī","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"مُلَـٰقٍ","english":"(will) meet","translit":"mulāqin","root":"لقي"},{"position":5,"arabic":"حِسَابِيَهْ","english":"my account","translit":"ḥisābiyah","root":"حسب"}]},{"number":21,"translation":"So he will be in a pleasant life -","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَهُوَ","english":"So he","translit":"fahuwa","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"فِى","english":"(will be) in","translit":"fī","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"عِيشَةٍۢ","english":"a life","translit":"ʿīshatin","root":"عيش"},{"position":4,"arabic":"رَّاضِيَةٍۢ","english":"pleasant","translit":"rāḍiyatin","root":"رضو"}]},{"number":22,"translation":"In an elevated garden,","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فِى","english":"In","translit":"fī","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"جَنَّةٍ","english":"a Garden","translit":"jannatin","root":"جنن"},{"position":3,"arabic":"عَالِيَةٍۢ","english":"elevated","translit":"ʿāliyatin","root":"علو"}]},{"number":23,"translation":"Its [fruit] to be picked hanging near.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"قُطُوفُهَا","english":"Its clusters of fruits","translit":"quṭūfuhā","root":"قطف"},{"position":2,"arabic":"دَانِيَةٌۭ","english":"hanging near","translit":"dāniyatun","root":"دنو"}]},{"number":24,"translation":"[They will be told], \"Eat and drink in satisfaction for what you put forth in the days past.\"","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"كُلُوا۟","english":"Eat","translit":"kulū","root":"أكل"},{"position":2,"arabic":"وَٱشْرَبُوا۟","english":"and drink","translit":"wa-ish'rabū","root":"شرب"},{"position":3,"arabic":"هَنِيٓـًٔۢا","english":"(in) satisfaction","translit":"hanīan","root":"هنأ"},{"position":4,"arabic":"بِمَآ","english":"for what","translit":"bimā","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"أَسْلَفْتُمْ","english":"you sent before you","translit":"aslaftum","root":"سلف"},{"position":6,"arabic":"فِى","english":"in","translit":"fī","root":""},{"position":7,"arabic":"ٱلْأَيَّامِ","english":"the days","translit":"l-ayāmi","root":"يوم"},{"position":8,"arabic":"ٱلْخَالِيَةِ","english":"past","translit":"l-khāliyati","root":"خلو"}]},{"number":25,"translation":"But as for he who is given his record in his left hand, he will say, \"Oh, I wish I had not been given my record","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَأَمَّا","english":"But as for","translit":"wa-ammā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"مَنْ","english":"(him) who","translit":"man","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"أُوتِىَ","english":"is given","translit":"ūtiya","root":"أتي"},{"position":4,"arabic":"كِتَـٰبَهُۥ","english":"his record","translit":"kitābahu","root":"كتب"},{"position":5,"arabic":"بِشِمَالِهِۦ","english":"in his left hand","translit":"bishimālihi","root":"شمل"},{"position":6,"arabic":"فَيَقُولُ","english":"will say","translit":"fayaqūlu","root":"قول"},{"position":7,"arabic":"يَـٰلَيْتَنِى","english":"O! I wish","translit":"yālaytanī","root":""},{"position":8,"arabic":"لَمْ","english":"not","translit":"lam","root":""},{"position":9,"arabic":"أُوتَ","english":"I had been given","translit":"ūta","root":"أتي"},{"position":10,"arabic":"كِتَـٰبِيَهْ","english":"my record","translit":"kitābiyah","root":"كتب"}]},{"number":26,"translation":"And had not known what is my account.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَلَمْ","english":"And not","translit":"walam","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"أَدْرِ","english":"I had known","translit":"adri","root":"دري"},{"position":3,"arabic":"مَا","english":"what","translit":"mā","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"حِسَابِيَهْ","english":"(is) my account","translit":"ḥisābiyah","root":"حسب"}]},{"number":27,"translation":"I wish my death had been the decisive one.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"يَـٰلَيْتَهَا","english":"O! I wish it","translit":"yālaytahā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"كَانَتِ","english":"had been","translit":"kānati","root":"كون"},{"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلْقَاضِيَةَ","english":"the end","translit":"l-qāḍiyata","root":"قضي"}]},{"number":28,"translation":"My wealth has not availed me.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"مَآ","english":"Not","translit":"mā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"أَغْنَىٰ","english":"has availed","translit":"aghnā","root":"غني"},{"position":3,"arabic":"عَنِّى","english":"me","translit":"ʿannī","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"مَالِيَهْ ۜ","english":"my wealth","translit":"māliyah","root":"مول"}]},{"number":29,"translation":"Gone from me is my authority.\"","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"هَلَكَ","english":"Is gone","translit":"halaka","root":"هلك"},{"position":2,"arabic":"عَنِّى","english":"from me","translit":"ʿannī","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"سُلْطَـٰنِيَهْ","english":"my authority","translit":"sul'ṭāniyah","root":"سلط"}]},{"number":30,"translation":"[Allah will say], \"Seize him and shackle him.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"خُذُوهُ","english":"Seize him","translit":"khudhūhu","root":"أخذ"},{"position":2,"arabic":"فَغُلُّوهُ","english":"and shackle him","translit":"faghullūhu","root":"غلل"}]},{"number":31,"translation":"Then into Hellfire drive him.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"ثُمَّ","english":"Then","translit":"thumma","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلْجَحِيمَ","english":"(into) the Hellfire","translit":"l-jaḥīma","root":"جحم"},{"position":3,"arabic":"صَلُّوهُ","english":"burn him","translit":"ṣallūhu","root":"صلي"}]},{"number":32,"translation":"Then into a chain whose length is seventy cubits insert him.\"","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"ثُمَّ","english":"Then","translit":"thumma","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"فِى","english":"into","translit":"fī","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"سِلْسِلَةٍۢ","english":"a chain","translit":"sil'silatin","root":"سلسل"},{"position":4,"arabic":"ذَرْعُهَا","english":"its length","translit":"dharʿuhā","root":"ذرع"},{"position":5,"arabic":"سَبْعُونَ","english":"(is) seventy","translit":"sabʿūna","root":"سبع"},{"position":6,"arabic":"ذِرَاعًۭا","english":"cubits","translit":"dhirāʿan","root":"ذرع"},{"position":7,"arabic":"فَٱسْلُكُوهُ","english":"insert him","translit":"fa-us'lukūhu","root":"سلك"}]},{"number":33,"translation":"Indeed, he did not used to believe in Allah, the Most Great,","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"إِنَّهُۥ","english":"Indeed, he","translit":"innahu","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"كَانَ","english":"was","translit":"kāna","root":"كون"},{"position":3,"arabic":"لَا","english":"not","translit":"lā","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"يُؤْمِنُ","english":"believing","translit":"yu'minu","root":"أمن"},{"position":5,"arabic":"بِٱللَّهِ","english":"in Allah","translit":"bil-lahi","root":"أله"},{"position":6,"arabic":"ٱلْعَظِيمِ","english":"the Most Great","translit":"l-ʿaẓīmi","root":"عظم"}]},{"number":34,"translation":"Nor did he encourage the feeding of the poor.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَلَا","english":"And (did) not","translit":"walā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"يَحُضُّ","english":"feel the urge","translit":"yaḥuḍḍu","root":"حضض"},{"position":3,"arabic":"عَلَىٰ","english":"on","translit":"ʿalā","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"طَعَامِ","english":"(the) feeding","translit":"ṭaʿāmi","root":"طعم"},{"position":5,"arabic":"ٱلْمِسْكِينِ","english":"(of) the poor","translit":"l-mis'kīni","root":"سكن"}]},{"number":35,"translation":"So there is not for him here this Day any devoted friend","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَلَيْسَ","english":"So not","translit":"falaysa","root":"ليس"},{"position":2,"arabic":"لَهُ","english":"for him","translit":"lahu","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلْيَوْمَ","english":"today","translit":"l-yawma","root":"يوم"},{"position":4,"arabic":"هَـٰهُنَا","english":"here","translit":"hāhunā","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"حَمِيمٌۭ","english":"any devoted friend","translit":"ḥamīmun","root":"حمم"}]},{"number":36,"translation":"Nor any food except from the discharge of wounds;","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَلَا","english":"And not","translit":"walā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"طَعَامٌ","english":"any food","translit":"ṭaʿāmun","root":"طعم"},{"position":3,"arabic":"إِلَّا","english":"except","translit":"illā","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"مِنْ","english":"from","translit":"min","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"غِسْلِينٍۢ","english":"(the) discharge of wounds","translit":"ghis'līnin","root":"غسل"}]},{"number":37,"translation":"None will eat it except the sinners.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"لَّا","english":"Not","translit":"lā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"يَأْكُلُهُۥٓ","english":"will eat it","translit":"yakuluhu","root":"أكل"},{"position":3,"arabic":"إِلَّا","english":"except","translit":"illā","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"ٱلْخَـٰطِـُٔونَ","english":"the sinners","translit":"l-khāṭiūna","root":"خطأ"}]},{"number":38,"translation":"So I swear by what you see","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَلَآ","english":"But nay","translit":"falā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"أُقْسِمُ","english":"I swear","translit":"uq'simu","root":"قسم"},{"position":3,"arabic":"بِمَا","english":"by what","translit":"bimā","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"تُبْصِرُونَ","english":"you see","translit":"tub'ṣirūna","root":"بصر"}]},{"number":39,"translation":"And what you do not see","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَمَا","english":"And what","translit":"wamā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"لَا","english":"not","translit":"lā","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"تُبْصِرُونَ","english":"you see","translit":"tub'ṣirūna","root":"بصر"}]},{"number":40,"translation":"[That] indeed, the Qur'an is the word of a noble Messenger.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"إِنَّهُۥ","english":"Indeed, it (is)","translit":"innahu","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"لَقَوْلُ","english":"surely (the) Word","translit":"laqawlu","root":"قول"},{"position":3,"arabic":"رَسُولٍۢ","english":"(of) a Messenger","translit":"rasūlin","root":"رسل"},{"position":4,"arabic":"كَرِيمٍۢ","english":"noble","translit":"karīmin","root":"كرم"}]},{"number":41,"translation":"And it is not the word of a poet; little do you believe.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَمَا","english":"And not","translit":"wamā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"هُوَ","english":"it","translit":"huwa","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"بِقَوْلِ","english":"(is the) word","translit":"biqawli","root":"قول"},{"position":4,"arabic":"شَاعِرٍۢ ۚ","english":"(of) a poet","translit":"shāʿirin","root":"شعر"},{"position":5,"arabic":"قَلِيلًۭا","english":"little","translit":"qalīlan","root":"قلل","audio":"wbw/069_041_006.mp3"},{"position":6,"arabic":"مَّا","english":"(is) what","translit":"mā","root":"","audio":"wbw/069_041_007.mp3"},{"position":7,"arabic":"تُؤْمِنُونَ","english":"you believe","translit":"tu'minūna","root":"أمن","audio":"wbw/069_041_008.mp3"}]},{"number":42,"translation":"Nor the word of a soothsayer; little do you remember.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَلَا","english":"And not","translit":"walā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"بِقَوْلِ","english":"(it is the) word","translit":"biqawli","root":"قول"},{"position":3,"arabic":"كَاهِنٍۢ ۚ","english":"(of) a soothsayer","translit":"kāhinin","root":"كهن"},{"position":4,"arabic":"قَلِيلًۭا","english":"little","translit":"qalīlan","root":"قلل","audio":"wbw/069_042_005.mp3"},{"position":5,"arabic":"مَّا","english":"(is) what","translit":"mā","root":"","audio":"wbw/069_042_006.mp3"},{"position":6,"arabic":"تَذَكَّرُونَ","english":"you take heed","translit":"tadhakkarūna","root":"ذكر","audio":"wbw/069_042_007.mp3"}]},{"number":43,"translation":"[It is] a revelation from the Lord of the worlds.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"تَنزِيلٌۭ","english":"(It is) a revelation","translit":"tanzīlun","root":"نزل"},{"position":2,"arabic":"مِّن","english":"from","translit":"min","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"رَّبِّ","english":"(the) Lord","translit":"rabbi","root":"ربب"},{"position":4,"arabic":"ٱلْعَـٰلَمِينَ","english":"(of) the worlds","translit":"l-ʿālamīna","root":"علم"}]},{"number":44,"translation":"And if Muhammad had made up about Us some [false] sayings,","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَلَوْ","english":"And if","translit":"walaw","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"تَقَوَّلَ","english":"he (had) fabricated","translit":"taqawwala","root":"قول"},{"position":3,"arabic":"عَلَيْنَا","english":"against Us","translit":"ʿalaynā","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"بَعْضَ","english":"some","translit":"baʿḍa","root":"بعض"},{"position":5,"arabic":"ٱلْأَقَاوِيلِ","english":"sayings","translit":"l-aqāwīli","root":"قول"}]},{"number":45,"translation":"We would have seized him by the right hand;","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"لَأَخَذْنَا","english":"Certainly We (would) have seized","translit":"la-akhadhnā","root":"أخذ"},{"position":2,"arabic":"مِنْهُ","english":"him","translit":"min'hu","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"بِٱلْيَمِينِ","english":"by the right hand","translit":"bil-yamīni","root":"يمن"}]},{"number":46,"translation":"Then We would have cut from him the aorta.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"ثُمَّ","english":"Then","translit":"thumma","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"لَقَطَعْنَا","english":"certainly We (would) have cut off","translit":"laqaṭaʿnā","root":"قطع"},{"position":3,"arabic":"مِنْهُ","english":"from him","translit":"min'hu","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"ٱلْوَتِينَ","english":"the aorta","translit":"l-watīna","root":"وتن"}]},{"number":47,"translation":"And there is no one of you who could prevent [Us] from him.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَمَا","english":"And not","translit":"famā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"مِنكُم","english":"from you","translit":"minkum","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"مِّنْ","english":"any","translit":"min","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"أَحَدٍ","english":"one","translit":"aḥadin","root":"أحد"},{"position":5,"arabic":"عَنْهُ","english":"[from him]","translit":"ʿanhu","root":""},{"position":6,"arabic":"حَـٰجِزِينَ","english":"(who could) prevent (it)","translit":"ḥājizīna","root":"حجز"}]},{"number":48,"translation":"And indeed, the Qur'an is a reminder for the righteous.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَإِنَّهُۥ","english":"And indeed, it","translit":"wa-innahu","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"لَتَذْكِرَةٌۭ","english":"(is) surely a reminder","translit":"latadhkiratun","root":"ذكر"},{"position":3,"arabic":"لِّلْمُتَّقِينَ","english":"for the Allah-fearing","translit":"lil'muttaqīna","root":"وقي"}]},{"number":49,"translation":"And indeed, We know that among you are deniers.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَإِنَّا","english":"And indeed, We","translit":"wa-innā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"لَنَعْلَمُ","english":"surely know","translit":"lanaʿlamu","root":"علم"},{"position":3,"arabic":"أَنَّ","english":"that","translit":"anna","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"مِنكُم","english":"among you","translit":"minkum","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"مُّكَذِّبِينَ","english":"(are) deniers","translit":"mukadhibīna","root":"كذب"}]},{"number":50,"translation":"And indeed, it will be [a cause of] regret upon the disbelievers.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَإِنَّهُۥ","english":"And indeed, it","translit":"wa-innahu","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"لَحَسْرَةٌ","english":"(is) surely a regret","translit":"laḥasratun","root":"حسر"},{"position":3,"arabic":"عَلَى","english":"upon","translit":"ʿalā","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"ٱلْكَـٰفِرِينَ","english":"the disbelievers","translit":"l-kāfirīna","root":"كفر"}]},{"number":51,"translation":"And indeed, it is the truth of certainty.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَإِنَّهُۥ","english":"And indeed, it (is)","translit":"wa-innahu","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"لَحَقُّ","english":"surely (the) truth","translit":"laḥaqqu","root":"حقق"},{"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلْيَقِينِ","english":"(of) certainty","translit":"l-yaqīni","root":"يقن"}]},{"number":52,"translation":"So exalt the name of your Lord, the Most Great.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَسَبِّحْ","english":"So glorify","translit":"fasabbiḥ","root":"سبح"},{"position":2,"arabic":"بِٱسْمِ","english":"(the) name","translit":"bi-is'mi","root":"سمو"},{"position":3,"arabic":"رَبِّكَ","english":"(of) your Lord","translit":"rabbika","root":"ربب"},{"position":4,"arabic":"ٱلْعَظِيمِ","english":"the Most Great","translit":"l-ʿaẓīmi","root":"عظم"}]}]}
